# Frequent collectors — hourly weather + air quality, 6h maritime/portugal
# Weather hourly for storm freshness (AEMET alerts change within minutes)
0 * * * * TASK=weather npx tsx index.ts 2>&1 && touch /tmp/last-run
0 */6 * * * TASK=maritime-forecast npx tsx index.ts 2>&1
0 */6 * * * TASK=portugal-weather npx tsx index.ts 2>&1

# MITECO national air quality (hourly — data has 7-8 week lag but worth checking)
30 * * * * TASK=air-quality npx tsx index.ts 2>&1

# CCAA real-time air quality — Madrid (20min cadence), Cataluña (daily)
*/20 * * * * TASK=air-quality-ccaa npx tsx index.ts 2>&1
